author: Dom Calicchio
title: California protest erupts over state’s coronavirus stay-at-home rules
description: A protest of more than 200 demonstrators broke out in Southern California on Friday against the state’s stay-at-home-orders in reaction to the coronavirus outbreak, according to reports.
